From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Samuel Attard <samuel.r.attard@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2020 14:39:52 -0700
Subject: build: add GN config

Adds BUILD.gn / filenames.gni so squirrel.mac can be built as part of
Electron's GN build, plus xcrun helpers and .gitignore tweaks for the
DEPS-managed vendor/ checkouts.

